        <div class="specialization-title">
          <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>
          Quality & Reliability
        </div>
        <p>Focus on quality control systems, statistical process control, and reliability engineering.</p>
        <ul class="features-list">
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> <span>Statistical quality control</span></li>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> <span>Six Sigma methodologies</span></li>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> <span>Reliability testing & analysis</span></li>
        </ul>
        <div class="resources-section">
          <div class="resources-title">Learning Resources</div>
          <ul class="channel-list">
