  <section>
    <h2 class="section-title">Core Concepts</h2>
    <div class="topics-grid">
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title"><i class="fas fa-tools"></i> Manufacturing Processes</div>
        <p>Understand traditional and advanced manufacturing methods including machining, forming, casting, and joining.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.coursera.org/learn/manufacturing-processes" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title"><i class="fas fa-clipboard-check"></i> Lean Manufacturing</div>
        <p>Master the principles of waste elimination, continuous improvement, and value stream optimization.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.edx.org/course/lean-production" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title"><i class="fas fa-drafting-compass"></i> CAD/CAM Systems</div>
        <p>Learn about computer-aided design and manufacturing tools for product development and production.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.coursera.org/learn/cad-cam-cae" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  
    <div class="topics-grid">
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title"><i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i> Quality Control</div>
        <p>Study statistical process control, inspection methods, and quality management systems.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.edx.org/course/statistical-quality-control" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title"><i class="fas fa-cubes"></i> Additive Manufacturing</div>
        <p>Understand 3D printing technologies, materials, and applications in production environments.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.coursera.org/learn/3d-printing-revolution" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
